snippet.title: Human Killing Machine gameplay (PC Game, 1988)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Human Killing Machine (aka hkm), Dos PC game produced by Tiertex in 1988 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/human-killing-machine/15785/
Human Killing Machine is a pretty good fighting game. You are a fighter and you have to go to different opponents from different countries.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
International Karate - https://youtu.be/hFtpgYJBZAE
Street Fighter - https://youtu.be/FJAAeCGyeFs
Aaargh! - https://youtu.be/A4GLNVJpt10
